citations:
    citation-acok-catelyn-i:
        source: source-acok
        properties:
            locator: "Catelyn I"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "POV: Catelyn Stark at Riverrun. Robb (age 15) holds court and dispatches Ser Cleos Frey with peace terms for Cersei. Olyvar Frey serves as Robb's squire. Brynden Tully (the Blackfish) reports on Lannister ravaging of the riverlands. Ser Stafford Lannister named as commander of new Lannister levies gathering at Casterly Rock; his son Ser Daven Lannister noted as more formidable. Hoster Tully dying in bed at Riverrun. Catelyn agrees to seek alliance with Renly Baratheon."
